// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-2483 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: e60df036-3036-5f37-b44e-9302ac94b581

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*photon os:1.0*" or process.executable like~ "*photon os:2.0*")
